{"tid":654216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重金娶泰仔】朝早着西裝 晚宴着婚紗 泰仔「出嫁」好轟動","createTime":"2018-05-05T12:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T12:32:03.000Z","uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"14c5e5d3aa63afde537e9408927b3c1633989f18","tid":654216,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"【重金娶泰仔】朝早着西裝 晚宴着婚紗 泰仔「出嫁」好轟動<br />\n\t<br />\n258,006<br />\n最後更新: 0505 18:33 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0505 12:03<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180505/large/1525492290_eed3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F1525492290_eed3.jpg&h=c14e5da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180505/large/1525492291_8642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F1525492291_8642.jpg&h=432968a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180505/large/1525492293_7a02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F1525492293_7a02.jpg&h=b6a9e514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t\t<br />\n<br />\n一名外籍男子日前重金迎娶同性的泰國戀人，「出嫁」的泰男早上以金色西裝帥氣登場，晚宴就換上婚紗豔壓四方，婚禮賓客均眼前一亮。<br />\n<br />\n婚禮在前天舉行，外籍男子帶同逾1,000萬泰銖（逾247萬港元）的聘禮，迎娶一名泰國男子，泰媒均以「美男子」形容「新娘」。聘禮包括現金100萬銖（約25萬港元）、一卡鑽石戒指、6銖重的黃金及房產地契等，出手闊綽。<br />\n<br />\n兩人當天上午按照泰式傳統行禮，「美男子」穿上金色西裝，與穿上金色傳統泰國新郎服飾的丈夫很相襯。到晚上「美男子」改化女妝，穿上一束高腰婚紗與伴侶一同進場接受賓客祝福，不論穿上男裝抑或女裝也毫不突兀。<br />\n<br />\n泰國網"},{"pid":"e2a2dbb5308f8798784019dd67fc4718f0de60be","tid":654216,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}